title: A Murder Is Announced - Agatha Christie
description:
5 X 30 Mins

June Whitfield plays Miss Marple in this Agatha Christie mystery.

An advert appears in a local newspaper, announcing that murder will take place at a local house that evening. An entire cast of suspects invite themselves to the house, assuming it to be a party, but at the appointed hour, an intruder is shot dead. Miss Marple investigates.......
